title: The Mightiest Duck
description: Buckle up Salt Shakers... you're in for a long one! Katie, Ashley, and Jay give their summaries of The Mighty Ducks franchise starting with D1 (37:19), then D2 (1:00:12), and lastly D3 (1:38:02). They also throw in a Challenge Update (1:36:58) and a Power Ranking of all three Mighty Ducks movies (2:14:28).
itunes:author: ESPN, Katie Nolan
itunes:subtitle: Have you ever wanted a lengthy summary of all three Mighty Duck movies? Well... now you have it!
